column2: select top #  p.specObjID, p.z, p.zErr, p.SRF, p.minSFR, p.maxSFR, s.logMass, s.logMass_err, s.Metallicity_mean, s.metallicity_err, t.Flux_Ha_#, t.Flux_Ha_#_Err, t.Flux_Hb_#, t.Flux_Hb_#_Err, t.Flux_OII_#, t.Flux_OII_#_Err, t.Flux_OIII_#, t.Flux_OIII_#_Err, t.Flux_OIII_#, t.Flux_OIII_#_Err, t.Flux_NII_#, t.Flux_NII_#_Err, t.Flux_SII_#, t.Flux_SII_#_Err, t.Flux_SII_#, t.Flux_SII_#_Err from  stellarMassStarformingPort p  JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyDust s ON s.specObjID = p.specObjID  JOIN emissionLinesPort t ON t.specObjID = s.specObjID  WHERE  p.z BETWEEN # AND # ORDER BY newid()
